plan_validation[1]{text,command,expected}:
  "Full Bun and isolated npm verification passed with 542 tests, enforced coverage floors, zero production vulnerabilities, frozen lock stability, packed npx/bunx execution, history audits, and valid workflow YAML.","bun run typecheck && bun run lint && bun run lint:strict && bun run build && bun run test && bun run test:coverage && bun run smoke:npx && bun run smoke:bunx && bun run audit:history && bun run audit:version-history",All checks pass on current working tree
plan_decisions[1]{ts,author,decision,rationale,evidence}:
  "2026-07-16T17:05:18.172Z",codex-root,Use native Dependabot Bun support and disable only commit body line length while retaining Conventional Commit subject validation.,"GitHub supports text bun.lock directly, and generated URLs cannot be meaningfully wrapped.",Actions runs 26767553085 and 26744281604 plus official GitHub Dependabot ecosystem documentation.
plan_discoveries[1]{ts,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T17:05:17.538Z",codex-root,"Dependabot used npm semantics against a Bun-owned repo, leaving bun.lock stale; generated commit bodies independently failed the body line-length rule."
